    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>paneer</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped paneer</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>paprika</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Tip: Only add half the cayenne pepper now, then taste later and add the rest if it needs more kick!</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>coated paneer</strong></p>",
